data.description: Adorable & Affordable 2-bed, 2-bath ranch, surrounded by a white picket fence. Why rent when you can own. Ideal for 1st time buyers, investors looking for income property or downsizers. Hardwood floors in bedrooms, a main bedroom with a private 1/2 bath, and adjacent bonus room for versatility. The living room features wood laminate floors, and the spacious eat-in kitchen includes a built-in breakfast bar and all appliances. What sets this property apart is the 3-car garage, equipped with a heating and cooling system perfect for car enthusiasts or hobbyists. Unfinished basement and crawl space provide room for future expansion. Take advantage of the Indiana Down Payment Assistance Program for a low-cost entry into homeownership. Conveniently located with easy access to expressways, shopping, and restaurants. Whether you're a first-time buyer, investor, or seeking a starter home, this property this cozy home is ready for immediate occupancy. Great way to start the new year!
